text: Morimus sexmaculipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1961. It is known from Malaysia.BioLib.cz - Morimus sexmaculipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 1961
